name: The Demon Busters
description:
Halloween is over. But it still leaves a number of creatures that are still roaming. It is the duty of the demon-busters to pursue and catch them all!

The scene is taken from my old Indonesian pixel art motion-comics entitled "Pendekar Cyborg - Bangkitnya Cyborg Kuntilanak Ngutang (Cyborg Warrior - Awakening of Cyborg Lady Satan)". 

A piece for celebrating #HEN500K event.
